  "body": "### Component\n\nForge, Cast\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nethers-rs http provider has a default polling interval of 7s, so sending a transaction and receiving the receipts takes at least 7s because the provider waits after the transactions was sent.\r\n\r\nThis is, so that we don't spam requests while waiting for confirmation(s) on inclusion (mainnet).\r\n\r\nwhen the endpoint is local, we can drastically lower that interval because:\r\n\r\na) likely a dev node so inclusion could be instantly\r\nb) unlikely to get ratelimited/blocked on local node\r\n\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
